{"name":"Sacred Ground","type":"move","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow-green.webp","system":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you perform a <strong>ritual of your religion</strong> to bless a <strong>small</strong> location...</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger Acolyte</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The area is [<em><strong>sacred</strong></em>] and [<em><strong>safe</strong></em>] as long as <strong>true believers</strong> of your cult dwell in it.</li>\n<li>Create <strong>one more <em>Tag</em></strong><em> </em>to represent your deity&rsquo;s recognizable influence upon the land. If you spend <strong>3 XP</strong> this effect will linger indefinitely.</li>\n<li>Say what could constitute an act of <strong>blasphemy </strong>for your deity. If such an act takes place within or nearby the blessed location, all <em><strong>Tags </strong></em>are either removed or inverted by the World.</li>\n</ul>","requiresMove":"Acolyte","moveType":"growth","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"success":{"key":"system.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":""},"partial":{"key":"system.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":""},"failure":{"key":"system.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Miss","value":""}},"uses":0,"playbook":"","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pbta","systemVersion":"0.7.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668548385255,"modifiedTime":1673106136403,"lastModifiedBy":"oNpcWyoIMSiMe9EN"},"_id":"45uCThAiphwqZHEm","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"oNpcWyoIMSiMe9EN":3}}
{"name":"Faith is My Strength","type":"move","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow-green.webp","system":{"name":"","description":"<p>When <strong>you pray</strong> to help someone with a task...</p>\n<p>Spend <strong>1 XP</strong>. You will always have an intuition of what they feel:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If they believe in your deity, they get an <em><strong>Advantage</strong></em>.</li>\n<li>If they don&rsquo;t, they get a <em><strong>Disadvantage</strong></em>.</li>\n<li>If they are honestly conflicted, they gain <strong>1 XP</strong>.</li>\n</ul>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"growth","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"success":{"key":"system.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":""},"partial":{"key":"system.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":""},"failure":{"key":"system.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Miss","value":""}},"uses":0,"playbook":"","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pbta","systemVersion":"0.7.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668549000214,"modifiedTime":1673106136402,"lastModifiedBy":"oNpcWyoIMSiMe9EN"},"_id":"6urmSzjb9V9j3qhb","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"oNpcWyoIMSiMe9EN":3}}
{"name":"God's Herald","type":"move","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow-green.webp","system":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you hold your <strong>divine icon</strong> aloft...</p>\n<p>If you invoke your deity&rsquo;s protection through it, spend <strong>XP</strong> then <em><strong>Threaten</strong></em> all hostile creatures within range.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Spend <strong>0 XP</strong>: [<em><strong>hand</strong></em>] range, with <strong>Temp </strong>force.</li>\n<li>Spend <strong>1 XP</strong>: [<em><strong>close</strong></em>] range, with <strong>Temp </strong>force.</li>\n<li>Spend <strong>2 XP</strong>: [<em><strong>reach</strong></em>] range, with <strong>Temp </strong>force.</li>\n<li>Spend <strong>5 XP</strong>: [<em><strong>reach</strong></em>] range, with <strong>Serious</strong> force.</li>\n</ul>","requiresMove":"","moveType":"growth","rollFormula":"","moveGroup":"","moveResults":{"success":{"key":"system.moveResults.success.value","label":"Success!","value":""},"partial":{"key":"system.moveResults.partial.value","label":"Partial Success","value":""},"failure":{"key":"system.moveResults.failure.value","label":"Miss","value":""}},"uses":0,"playbook":"","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"choices":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pbta","systemVersion":"0.7.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668549793778,"modifiedTime":1673106136402,"lastModifiedBy":"oNpcWyoIMSiMe9EN"},"_id":"EBsbweUG3gGv8A10","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"oNpcWyoIMSiMe9EN":3}}
